data.description: NEW PRICE! Live your Florida dream! The Port Royal model is nestled in the beautiful community of Solivita, this immaculate home is move-in ready with many outstanding amenities. A beautiful two-bedroom, two-bath home features an updated kitchen with contemporary glass tile backsplash and under-counter lighting as well as a large walk-in pantry. A large extra 410 sq ft enclosed air-conditioned all-season Florida room and updated bathrooms with illuminated and defogging mirrors in the Master Bath, and a large owner suite as well as lots of closet space throughout the home. In addition, there is an office/study which could be easily transformed into a third bedroom, if desired. Enjoy cool breezes on a screened front porch as well as a covered back porch for your outdoor grilling and a large two-car garage with prewiring for a golf cart charger. Other features include remote-controlled lighting throughout the main living area and double-pane glass windows in this beautiful home. Never Be Without Power during inclement weather as this home has an extra bonus, it is wired for a generator with a separate breaker box and includes a generator.  A prewired alarm system and a rear photo electric light provide security around the clock. The home is situated at the beginning of a Cul de Sac, so no through traffic annoyance. Solivita is a lushly landscaped community with many beautiful water features throughout and offers many outstanding amenities.  Enjoy the two-championship golf courses, the spa and fitness center, 14 pools, tennis, basketball, and pickleball courts, 3 restaurants, and a pharmacy all located in this wonderful guard gated community.  Come see this wonderful home, today!
